quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  10,43,"Waminhum man yanthuru ilaykaafaanta tahdee alAAumya walaw kanoo la yubsiroon"
  10,44,"Inna Allaha la yathlimuannasa shay-an walakinna annasaanfusahum yathlimoon"
  10,45,"Wayawma yahshuruhum kaan lamyalbathoo illa saAAatan mina annahariyataAAarafoona baynahum qad khasira allatheena kaththaboobiliqa-i Allahi wama kanoo muhtadeen"
  10,46,"Wa-imma nuriyannaka baAAdaallathee naAAiduhum aw natawaffayannaka fa-ilaynamarjiAAuhum thumma Allahu shaheedun AAala mayafAAaloon"
  10,47,"Walikulli ommatin rasoolun fa-itha jaarasooluhum qudiya baynahum bilqisti wahum layuthlamoon"
  10,48,"Wayaqooloona mata hathaalwaAAdu in kuntum sadiqeen"
  10,49,"Qul la amliku linafsee darranwala nafAAan illa ma shaa Allahulikulli ommatin ajalun itha jaa ajaluhum falayasta/khiroona saAAatan wala yastaqdimoon"
  10,50,"Qul araaytum in atakum AAathabuhubayatan aw naharan matha yastaAAjilu minhualmujrimoon"
  10,51,"Athumma itha ma waqaAAa amantumbihi al-ana waqad kuntum bihi tastaAAjiloon"
  10,52,"Thumma qeela lillatheena thalamoothooqoo AAathaba alkhuldi hal tujzawna illabima kuntum taksiboon"
  10,53,"Wayastanbi-oonaka ahaqqun huwa qul eewarabbee innahu lahaqqun wama antum bimuAAjizeen"
